INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('563', '5', '2016-09-27 23:24:39', '2016-09-27 23:24:39', '<strong>MRC Luxury River Expeditions</strong>\n\nYour Chi, your Energy, your Mind Body &amp; Soul are in safe hands. Welcome to Mekong River Cruiser &amp; your fleet of Viet Cruises.\n\nWho are we and who are you ?\n\nWell to begin with, you always come first!\n\nSo we believe you to be well travelled, seasoned travellers. You have a zest for life and living the great outdoors. To explore South East Asia, at any age, is not for the faint hearted – it’s for the adventurous. Be prepared to step off the beaten track and step back in time. Welcome to Indochina.!\n\nYou are of mixed nationalities, cosmopolitan in fact and have a myriad of personal tastes, likes &amp; dislikes - all matched with your individual needs, wants and expectations of a classic Asian sojourn. Dream on… We are here, waiting to welcome you…!\n\nWho are we? We believe we are the ‘chosen ones’…. those who have chosen to attend to your personal needs, 24 hours daily, 7 days weekly. We are those East &amp; Western eclectic group of individuals who live and work harmoniously together, as a dynamic team to quite simply, look after you!\n\nTake this as another “guarantee of service”.\n\nWhat should you expect of your Vietnam and Cambodian odyssey adventure - all things that is Mekong River Cruiser.\n\nSo naturally, expect the unexpected.\n\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '174-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-09-27 23:24:39', '2016-09-27 23:24:39', '', '174', 'https://www.vietcruises.com/uncategorized/174-autosave-v1-563.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('564', '5', '2016-09-27 23:24:49', '2016-09-27 23:24:49', '<strong>MRC Luxury River Expeditions</strong>\r\n\r\nYour Chi, your Energy, your Mind Body &amp; Soul are in safe hands. Welcome to Mekong River Cruiser &amp; your fleet of Viet Cruises.\r\n\r\nWho are we and who are you ?\r\n\r\nWell to begin with, you always come first!\r\n\r\nSo we believe you to be well travelled, seasoned travellers. You have a zest for life and living the great outdoors. To explore South East Asia, at any age, is not for the faint hearted – it’s for the adventurous. Be prepared to step off the beaten track and step back in time. Welcome to Indochina.!\r\n\r\nYou are of mixed nationalities, cosmopolitan in fact and have a myriad of personal tastes, likes &amp; dislikes - all matched with your individual needs, wants and expectations of a classic Asian sojourn. Dream on… We are here, waiting to welcome you…!\r\n\r\nWho are we? We believe we are the ‘chosen ones’…. those who have chosen to attend to your personal needs, 24 hours daily, 7 days weekly. We are those East &amp; Western eclectic group of individuals who live and work harmoniously together, as a dynamic team to quite simply, look after you!\r\n\r\nTake this as another “guarantee of service”.\r\n\r\nWhat should you expect of your Vietnam and Cambodian odyssey adventure - all things that is Mekong River Cruiser.\r\n\r\nSo naturally, expect the unexpected.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '174-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-27 23:24:49', '2016-09-27 23:24:49', '', '174', 'https://www.vietcruises.com/uncategorized/174-revision-v1-564.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('565', '5', '2016-10-29 16:17:31', '2016-10-29 09:17:31', '….Welcome to Southern Vietnam….\n\nThe ultimate journey of exploration, along the lower Mekong, is to cruise from Saigon Port through the waterways of the famous Mekong Delta and then head north into Cambodian waters. By combining shipboard life, in elegant French colonial luxury, with discreet and fascinating shore excursions, this is the most intimate way to be ‘up close and personal’ with the people and culture of Southern Vietnam.\n\nFeed your senses. Savour the extraordinary sights, sounds, smells and tastes of remote location river cruise life. This is also a journey of sensory awareness and personal enlightenment.\n\nFor 7 nights and 8 days, your crew of young proud Cambodians &amp; Vietnamese sailors will take delicate care of all your needs, wants and expectations, every nautical mile along the way.\n\nIt’s time to cross the border between Vietnam and Cambodia. From the delta’s lush dense bountiful vegetation and the rice paddies of Vietnam’s “rice bowl”, the scenery starts to change.\n\n…..Welcome to Cambodia….\n\nEqually as exotic and by comparison to Vietnam, the plains of Cambodia open before you as we cruise upstream towards the nation’s capital of Phnom Penh. Along the riverbanks the oxen-carts plough their way along a narrow path, working the land, forever contributing to the cooperative, subsistence way of Life that is Cambodia today and yesteryear.', 'Mekong Classic 7 nights and 8 days Ho Chi Minh - Siem R', 'From departure in Saigon Port, to arrival in Angkor Wat seven days later,\nyou would have a lifetime of memories, of sights and sounds, of smells and tastes that make up the fabulous Mekong Delta.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '85-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-10-29 16:17:31', '2016-10-29 09:17:31', '', '85', 'https://www.vietcruises.com/uncategorized/85-autosave-v1-565.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
