INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('604', '5', '2016-10-24 21:23:16', '2016-10-24 14:23:16', 'The River Vessel (RV) Mekong Princess is sixty-five meters in length with a seven-meter beam (width). She is powered by two 480 HP Doosan Marine engines and can cruise at a top speed of eleven knots (20 kms per hour). The average cruising speed is 8 knots (approximately 15 kms per hour). Built in Port Saigon to international design and safety standards, RV Mekong Princess was launched in 2015 and is considered the best-constructed and most elegant vessel plying the waters of the Mekong River today.', 'Mekong Princess', 'The Mekong River is the source of life for the people of the nations through which she flows: they live, work, eat, sleep, and even shop on her surface and along her banks. The traditional, floating markets of Can Tho, Vietnam, offer a colorful look at the daily life on the river, bringing farmers from surrounding areas to sell or trade their produce to local restaurants, local families, and other farmers. Many Buddhist monasteries in Cambodia are built near the river to serve the rural communities in the education of their children. In the center of it all is Phnom Penh, a city of stark contrasts between the rural and urban, the fast and slow, and the rich and poor.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '65-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-10-24 21:23:16', '2016-10-24 14:23:16', '', '65', 'https://www.vietcruises.com/uncategorized/65-autosave-v1-604.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('605', '5', '2016-10-04 04:59:42', '2016-10-04 04:59:42', '<strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE</strong>\n\nTerms and Conditions apply to all vessels under MRC Ltd. operation unless otherwise noted. Any and all information contained herein is in effect at the time of printing and is subject to change at any time. Information contained in this brochure does not form  INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('606', '5', '2016-10-04 05:00:13', '2016-10-04 05:00:13', '<strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE</strong>\r\n\r\nTerms and Conditions apply to all vessels under MRC Ltd. operation unless otherwise noted. Any and all information contained herein is in effect at the time of printing and is subject to change at any time. Information contained in this brochure does not form  INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('607', '5', '2016-10-04 08:58:30', '2016-10-04 08:58:30', '<strong>MRC Luxury River Expeditions</strong>\r\n\r\nUnlike most other hotels, resorts and cruise ships, this is not “Our” exotic expedition - it is all ‘Yours’. It is not our manner to tell you what to do, when to do it, or how to enjoy yourselves. We are quite simply your facilitators, your guides, hosts &amp; hostesses. We are all focused and passionate about providing you with a heart-warming “Once in a Life-time” truly unique and exotic Asian adventure holiday. Welcome to Mekong River Cruiser.\r\n\r\nYes - we provide all ‘mod-cons’ and state of the art luxury, but you certainly expect that in a boutique five star environment nowadays. Yes - we present an array of room amenities and guest facilities that are second to none in the country, if not the region. So what makes us special..?\r\n\r\nHumbly, we offer our “guarantee of service”…. quiet, understated, efficient; discerning like you. And then again, those extra special touches that makes for that extra special attention to detail.\r\n\r\nAs Rudyard Kipling once said; “The trip, the journey, the fulfilment will be yours…”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '174-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-04 08:58:30', '2016-10-04 08:58:30', '', '174', 'https://www.vietcruises.com/uncategorized/174-revision-v1-607.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
